Symbols

$\in$

{% raw %}
  • $\in$ denotes set membership - we write $x \in X$ if $x$ is an element of the set $X$.
{% endraw %}

$\setminus$

{% raw %}
  • $\setminus$ denotes set difference.
{% endraw %}

$\{a\}$

{% raw %}
